1 - Install Kivy Launcher app (https://apkpure.com/kivy-launcher/org.kivy.pygame)

2 - Create a folder named kivy in the system storage

3 - Paste your project into kivy folder (Your main aplication must called main.py)

4 - Create a file named android.txt inside your project folder with the content:
title=<Application Title>
author=<Your Name>
orientation=<portrait|landscape>

5 - Open the Kivy Launcher and run the application